have the people join your network, and when the join the hamachi network the must spell the network name perfectly or else it will say network could not be found, then when the load up moparscape get then to click File>New port and they must put in the port it says on your server, which should look like
Server start on 0.0.0.0 43594< in that case 43594 would be your port, then all they have to do is go File>New Server on moparscape and put in your hamachi IP, then they are good to go
